p.k: In the third episode of the set we meet the real enthusiasts of off-road. Assisting in the training, preparations in the workshop, and participating in a cross-country rally
p.d: In the third episode of the set we meet the real enthusiasts of off-road. Assisting in the training, preparations in the workshop, and participating in a cross-country rally, we learn how to prepare the car and the crew to get through the difficult terrain. We talk about the necessary skills, driving technique, and how to start such an extreme adventure by yourself.
